Invariants & Properties (Please verify / refine)

1. Receipt immutability: No mutation or deletion; unique IDs; causal linkages (job→escrow→release→tax).


2. Escrow safety: No double-spend; no premature release; all paths end with either worker or refund, never both.


3. Tax correctness: Withholding applied deterministically at release; jurisdiction tag attached (oracle-fed).


4. UBI discipline: Never exceeds 70% of 90d inflows; runway ≥12 months or UBI auto-scales down.


5. Override limits: Only Presidency key can invoke; emits event; expires ≤30d unless ratified; cannot bypass treasury/UBI caps.


6. Voting uniqueness: One-human-one-vote via World ID proof; AIs/robots excluded from voting unless future law enables.


7. Reputation resistance: Stake-weighted + decay; low-value job spam excluded; wash trading slashes stake.


8. Investment guards: Allocation bands enforced; vol cap & liquidity floor enforced on-chain; rebalancing only with quorum oracles.


9. Lottery fairness: Buy-in only; eligibility gates; VRF randomness; deterministic payout splits; 20% to treasury.


10. Safe Reboot: 3-of-5, time-locked; cannot move funds; only restores validators / pauses risky modules.




